January 15, 2018 / 5:29 AM / Updated 31 minutes ago Xiaomi mandates Citic Securities, Morgan Stanley, Goldman Sachs for IPO - IFR Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
HONG KONG (Reuters) - Chinese smartphone maker Xiaomi has picked Citic Securities, Goldman Sachs and Morgan Stanley as joint sponsors for its proposed IPO, IFR reported. FILE PHOTO: A journalist takes picture of Xiaomi's new mobile phone Mi Max at its launch in Beijing, May 10, 2016. REUTERS/Kim Kyung-Hoon/File Photo 
